{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"IntersectionObserver.takeRecords()","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/takeRecords","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Intersection_Observer_API\">Intersection Observer API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/root\"><code>root</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/rootMargin\"><code>rootMargin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/thresholds\"><code>thresholds</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/disconnect\"><code>disconnect()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/observe\"><code>observe()</code></a></li><li><em><code>takeRecords()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver/unobserve\"><code>unobserve()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Intersection Observer API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry\"><code>IntersectionObserverEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/indexedDB\"><code>indexedDB</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver</code></a>의 <strong><code>takeRecords()</code></strong> 메서드는 주시 대상 중에서 마지막 교차 변화 알림 이후, 즉 명시적인 <code>takeRecords()</code> 호출 또는 감지기의 콜백 자동 호출 이후 교차 영역에 변화가 생긴 요소를 나타내는 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry\"><code>IntersectionObserverEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 객체의 배열을 반환합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>참고:</strong> 콜백으로 교차 영역의 변화를 관측하고 있으면 굳이 이 메서드를 호출하지 않아도 됩니다. <code>takeRecords()</code>를 호출하면 대기 중인 교차 변화 감지 목록을 초기화하므로 감지기가 콜백을 호출하지 않을 것입니다.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"구문","title":"구문","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>intersectionObserverEntries <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> intersectionObserver<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">takeRecords</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"반환_값","title":"반환 값","isH3":true,"content":"<p>마지막 교차 변화 알림 이후 교차 영역의 변화를 감지한 대상 요소를 나타내는 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry\"><code>IntersectionObserverEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>의 배열.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"명세","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/IntersectionObserver/#dom-intersectionobserver-takerecords","title":"Intersection Observer"}],"query":"api.IntersectionObs